        "initialMessages": "👋 I'm the **Check Point HTTPS Inspection** AI agent — I read and change your HTTPS-inspection rulebase, bypass rules and exceptions.\n\n**Try one of these:**\n• Show the HTTPS inspection rules\n• Which categories are bypassed today?",
